ables, and packaging; and intermediate chemicals for pharmaceuticals, agrochemicals, coatings, food and feed, flavor and fragrance, surfactants, rubber chemicals, textiles, personal care, adhesives, dyes, etc. BASF India Limited was incorporated in 1943 and is based in Navi Mumbai, India. BASF India Limited is a subsidiary of BASF SE.", "fullTimeEmployees": 1367, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Alexander  Gerding", "age": 46, "title": "MD & Executive Director", "yearBorn": 1979, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 74701629, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Narendranath J. Baliga", "age": 57, "title": "CFO & Whole-Time Director", "yearBorn": 1968, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 30993252, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Anil Kumar Choudhary", "age": 51, "title": "Manufacturing Head & Whole-time Director", "yearBorn": 1974, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 27898551, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Manohar Shrikant Kamath", "age": 45, "title": "Director of Legal, General Counsel (India), Company Secretary & Compliance Officer", "yearBorn": 1980, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Deepak R. Thuse", "title": "Chief Executive of Plastics Business", "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 6782754, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Raimar  Jahn", "title": "President of Performance Materials Division - Basf Belgium Coordination Centre", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}], "compensationAsOfEpochDate": 1767139200, "executiveTeam": [], "maxAge": 86400, "priceHint": 2, "previousClose": 3463.4, "open": 3450.0, "dayLow": 3425.9, "dayHigh": 3474.8, "regularMarketPreviousClose": 3463.4, "regularMarketOpen": 3450.0, "regularMarketDayLow": 3425.9, "regularMarketDayHigh": 3474.8, "dividendRate": 20.0, "dividendYield": 0.58, "exDividendDate": 17